            <h3>Location</h3>
            <span>Ocala, FL</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="contact-cta">
        <div class="cta-card">
          <h3>Open to Opportunities</h3>
          <p>
            I am looking for my next challenge in platform engineering or SRE. 
            I want to join a team where I can help build infrastructure that 
            makes a real difference.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-interests">
            <span class="interest-tag">Platform Engineering</span>
            <span class="interest-tag">Site Reliability</span>
            <span class="interest-tag">Cloud Architecture</span>
            <span class="interest-tag">DevOps</span>
            <span class="interest-tag">Agentic AI</span>
          </div>
          <a href="mailto:WilliamValdez22@gmail.com" class="btn btn-primary">
            Send me an email
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
